{"thag12.2:0.1":"Theragatha 12.2 ","thag12.2:0.2":"Dvadasakanipata ","thag12.2:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag12.2:0.4":"Sunitattheragatha ","thag12.2:1.1":"“Nice kulamhi jatoham, ","thag12.2:1.2":"daliddo appabhojano; ","thag12.2:1.3":"Hinakammam mamam asi, ","thag12.2:1.4":"ahosim pupphachaddako. ","thag12.2:2.1":"Jigucchito manussanam, ","thag12.2:2.2":"paribhuto ca vambhito; ","thag12.2:2.3":"Nicam manam karitvana, ","thag12.2:2.4":"vandissam bahukam janam. ","thag12.2:3.1":"Athaddasasim sambuddham, ","thag12.2:3.2":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhatam; ","thag12.2:3.3":"Pavisantam mahaviram, ","thag12.2:3.4":"magadhanam puruttamam. ","thag12.2:4.1":"Nikkhipitvana byabhangim, ","thag12.2:4.2":"vanditum upasankamim; ","thag12.2:4.3":"Mameva anukampaya, ","thag12.2:4.4":"atthasi purisuttamo. ","thag12.2:5.1":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","thag12.2:5.2":"ekamantam thito tada; ","thag12.2:5.3":"Pabbajjam ahamayacim, ","thag12.2:5.4":"sabbasattanamuttamam. ","thag12.2:6.1":"Tato karuniko sattha, ","thag12.2:6.2":"sabbalokanukampako; ","thag12.2:6.3":"‘Ehi bhikkhu’ti mam aha, ","thag12.2:6.4":"sa me asupasampada. ","thag12.2:7.1":"Soham eko arannasmim, ","thag12.2:7.2":"viharanto atandito; ","thag12.2:7.3":"Akasim satthu vacanam, ","thag12.2:7.4":"yatha mam ovadi jino. ","thag12.2:8.1":"Rattiya pathamam yamam, ","thag12.2:8.2":"Pubbajatimanussarim; ","thag12.2:8.3":"Rattiya majjhimam yamam, ","thag12.2:8.4":"Dibbacakkhum visodhayim; ","thag12.2:8.5":"Rattiya pacchime yame, ","thag12.2:8.6":"Tamokhandham padalayim. ","thag12.2:9.1":"Tato ratya vivasane, ","thag12.2:9.2":"suriyassuggamanam pati; ","thag12.2:9.3":"Indo brahma ca agantva, ","thag12.2:9.4":"mam namassimsu panjali. ","thag12.2:10.1":"‘Namo te purisajanna, ","thag12.2:10.2":"namo te purisuttama; ","thag12.2:10.3":"Yassa te asava khina, ","thag12.2:10.4":"dakkhineyyosi marisa’. ","thag12.2:11.1":"Tato disvana mam sattha, ","thag12.2:11.2":"devasanghapurakkhatam; ","thag12.2:11.3":"Sitam patukaritvana, ","thag12.2:11.4":"imamattham abhasatha. ","thag12.2:12.1":"‘Tapena brahmacariyena, ","thag12.2:12.2":"samyamena damena ca; ","thag12.2:12.3":"Etena brahmano hoti, ","thag12.2:12.4":"etam brahmanamuttaman’”ti. ","thag12.2:12.5":"… Sunito thero … ","thag12.2:12.6":"Dvadasakanipato nitthito. ","thag12.2:13.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag12.2:13.1":"Silava ca sunito ca, ","thag12.2:13.2":"thera dve te mahiddhika; ","thag12.2:13.3":"Dvadasamhi nipatamhi, ","thag12.2:13.4":"gathayo catuvisatiti. "}